Our Mission

Changing Lives for Good through proclaiming the Good News of Jesus Christ!

CCFM has introduced thousands of people to Jesus and thousands more have re-dedicated their lives back to Christ as a result of listening to the station. Since the inception of CCFm, thousands upon thousands of calls were made to our 24/7prayer line.
